Running command: python - <<'PY'
import requests
# try to query collections list for dataset
base='https://api.cellxgene.cziscience.com/dp/v1/collections'
r=requests.get(base, timeout=10).json()
print('num collections', len(r['collections']))
# take first public collection id, get details endpoint maybe /collections/<id>
id=r['collections'][0]['id']
url=f'https://api.cellxgene.cziscience.com/dp/v1/collections/{id}'
r2=requests.get(url, timeout=10)
print('collection detail status', r2.status_code)
print(r2.text[:200])
